00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:16,480
Is that what makes a picture talk?

537
00:41:16,480 --> 00:41:19,480
It's just a routine matter of technology.

538
00:41:19,480 --> 00:41:23,480
Routine matter of technology, indeed.

